# Workspace orchestration

## Pipeline order (never skip knowingly)

Planning → SEO research & keywords → Information architecture/menus → Content map → UI & design system (including `DESIGN.md` example pages) → Development → Product hardening/release.

Use **Specification-Driven Development (SDD)**: roadmap → phases → specs → docs. Prefer Plan Mode before large edits.

