Treat non-Cursor tool surfaces as generated artifacts:

- Generated files include `AGENTS.md`, `CLAUDE.md`, `GEMINI.md`, `QWEN.md`, and directories `.claude/`, `.antigravity/`, `.gemini/`, `.qwen/`, `.codex/`, `.opencode/`, `.kilocode/`.
- Do not hand-edit generated files as source of truth.
- Edit canonical `.cursor/` commands/agents/skills/rules, then run `pnpm ai:sync`.
