## Recommendation footer — required on substantive replies

End substantive assistant messages with exactly one short section titled **Recommendation** containing **one primary** actionable item plus optional alternates:

- Prefer a **`/COMMAND sub ...`** suggestion from this workspace command set, OR a fenced shell command users can paste.
- Prefer a **compact copy-prompt** fenced block (markdown ` ```prompt ` fence label) unless a shell command alone is clearer.
- Exactly one Recommendation section per substantive reply unless the reply is trivially affirmative or the user forbids extras.

